race.description: 1Equine - For The Equine Athlete Maiden Handicap
race.comment: SPIRITOFTHEWORLD (10) showed good early dash at Warwick before fading out of it. He likely had an issue there and assess his chances on the near miss at Gatton prior. Comes back to a shorter sprint freshened up, and expect a much better effort. BRAVE LIKE LILY (4) debuts and owns a Dalby trial win. She maps well from a handy gate on her home deck and Savva sticks from the trials. Everything points to a forward showing on debut. I AM PIETRA (5) debuted on a heavy track at Gatton, beaten 2L. She's sure to build on that and will be every chance from an inside barrier. TROOPER SAM (11) peaks and would be around the mark putting his best foot forward.
